            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "筲箕灣錢大媽女工切肉「失手」 誤削指頭送院救治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"女工切傷手，警在場調查。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/819b09d76312167d70ee86340e890553/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040312115749342.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">女工切傷手，警在場調查。蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（3日）早上10時51分，連鎖超市「錢大媽」位於筲箕灣道98號的分店，一名女店員在肉枱切肉時不慎切傷手，左手中指皮開肉綻，部分手指頭皮肉被切去。她痛極呼叫，其他店員見狀連忙報警。救護員接報到場，即場為受傷女店員包紮傷口後，將她送往東區醫院救治。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174582/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女店員在肉枱切肉時，切去左手中指部分皮肉。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32124e8e5dd7540d8e972a26a0895f71/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_114645830_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女店員在肉枱切肉時，切去左手中指部分皮肉。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174584/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0dcdb7e765fb9782e5fdef727ca8826d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_114645830_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174585/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場是錢大媽的筲箕灣分店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96a7ab59dbbd404ea59354b1b7dfe1be/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_114645830_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場是錢大媽的筲箕灣分店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174586/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33941d624fa54bf14183d200f3c56351/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_114645830_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174587/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/81550b4b42fba96844596e1dd8a2dc85/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_114645830_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
