        {
            "title": "英超｜拉舒福特又入波 助維拉3蛋炒白禮頓 烏尼：佢重拾信心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f83e99f52c9566648d11f2c6143c9092/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040311542212448.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>被曼聯棄用外借至阿士東維拉的拉舒福特，表現逐步回升，繼上場足總盃梅開二度後，於周三英超又入波，首為維拉於聯賽建功，助球隊作客3:0大勝白禮頓，主帥烏尼賽後即大讚此子開始重拾信心。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b49d06562851bdd9d9af3699ff3906e/2025-04/2025-04-02T195749Z_3949602_UP1EL421JGBZY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2342aef310fea2a288190cf15761c16c/2025-04/2025-04-02T195725Z_635813806_UP1EL421JFNZS_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fde543ba3aa5dc3dd408a74dee799276/2025-04/2025-04-02T195636Z_549728608_UP1EL421JEBZO_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b13ac2b3a6114af18de9b46b0bfbd675/2025-04/2025-04-02T195710Z_807896953_UP1EL421JF9ZQ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特連續兩場入波。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db32cd50f4e2fc7c924abf29cad352a9/2025-04/2025-04-02T193213Z_795060299_UP1EL421I9NXM_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/56acd7c4b6253a1621724a12cafb1ca9/2025-04/2025-04-02T202444Z_1090451905_UP1EL421KP63T_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d0356033aee89d3621d29d0cad8f6d4/2025-04/2025-04-02T205023Z_267832851_UP1EL421LVX7J_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BHA-AVL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿士東維拉擊敗白禮頓。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>拉舒福特連續2場入波</h2>\n<p>拉舒福特於上場足總盃獨取兩球，取得外借至維拉後的首個入球，助球隊3:0贏普雷斯頓入4強。今仗他延續勇態，於下半場士哥為球隊先開紀錄，取得個人自去年12月後首個英超入球，加上馬高阿辛斯奧和當耶爾馬倫的入球，助維拉作客3:0擊敗白禮頓。\n\n</p><h2>烏尼：拉舒福特重拾信心</h2>\n<p>自被外借至阿士東維拉後，拉舒福特狀態回升，至今為新東家上陣11場已貢獻3個入球和4次助攻，早前更重返英格蘭國家隊。維拉主帥烏尼賽後大讚此子道：「我叫他繼續努力。隨著上場時間愈多，他的身體狀況愈好，現在也有更多入球。我們試圖利用他的特質，他現在正處於最有自信的時刻。最重要的是他的感覺如何，開始恢復自信，專注於足球，並與隊友愈來愈融洽。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
